Package org.gbif.api.model.event.search

Class EventSearchParameter

java.lang.Object
org.gbif.api.model.event.search.EventSearchParameter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, SearchParameter
public class EventSearchParameter extends Object implements SearchParameter, Serializable
Supported query parameters by the occurrence search and download service. For download predicates only the numerical types support comparisons other than equals.
